    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>An oily liquid ketone used as an industrial solvent for paints, coatings and plastics. It is also used to clean metals, remove spots in fabrics, and as an activator in oxidation reactions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
